OL,3,CForce 'considering next steps' after
OL,4,Cit discriminated against white officers
OL,6,FThames Valley Police has said it is
OL,7,F"carefully considering next steps"
OL,8,Fafter losing an employment tribunal
OL,9,Fcase.
OL,11,FIn an attempt to improve the diversity
OL,12,Fof its senior staff, a superintendent
OL,13,Fwas told to "make it happen" by
OL,14,Fappointing an "Asian" sergeant to the
OL,15,Frank of detective inspector without
OL,16,Fholding any competitive process.
