OL,3,CForce 'considering next steps' after
OL,4,Cit discriminated against white officers
OL,6,FAfter taking the force to an
OL,7,Femployment tribunal, three police
OL,8,Fofficers won their case after claiming
OL,9,Fto have been passed over for promotion
OL,10,Fbecause they were "white British".
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Phillip Turner-
OL,13,FRobson, Inspector Graham Horton and
OL,14,FKirsteen Bishop, a custody inspector,
OL,15,Fhad been working with the force for
OL,16,Fbetween 19 and 26 years when they were
OL,17,Fblocked from applying for the role,
OL,18,Fthe employment tribunal was told.
OL,26,@rD@SOUrD@aO]
