OL,6,FThe tribunal heard that in August
OL,7,F2022, plans were discussed for a job
OL,8,Fadvert, for a detective inspector in
OL,9,Fthe force's "priority crime team" at
OL,10,FAylesbury, to be put out.
OL,12,FHaving been made aware of the vacancy,
OL,13,FMr Turner-Robson expressed his
OL,14,Finterest on the same day.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@aO]
