OL,3,CForce 'considering next steps' after
OL,4,Cit discriminated against white officers
OL,6,FBut the following month,
OL,7,FSuperintendent Emma Baillie made the
OL,8,Fdecision to move Sergeant Sidhu, whose
OL,9,Ffirst name was not provided, into the
OL,10,Frole without undertaking any
OL,11,Fcompetitive process or advertising the
OL,12,Fvacancy to staff, the tribunal was
OL,13,Ftold.
OL,15,FThe superintendent had been told to
OL,16,F"make it happen" by the deputy chief
OL,17,Fconstable and "took the decision
OL,18,Fwithout thinking it through", the
OL,19,Ftribunal said.
