OL,3,CForce 'considering next steps' after
OL,4,Cit discriminated against white officers
OL,6,FEmployment Judge Robin Postle
OL,7,Fconcluded that the three white
OL,8,Fofficers were directly discriminated
OL,9,Fagainst by reason of the protected
OL,10,Fcharacteristic of race.
OL,12,F"The superintendent made a decision to
OL,13,Fmove Police Sergeant Sidhu into the
OL,14,Fdetective inspector role without any
OL,15,Fcompetitive assessment process taking
OL,16,Fplace," the Judge said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@GO]
