OL,3,CForce 'considering next steps' after
OL,4,Cit discriminated against white officers
OL,6,F"It went beyond mere encouragement,
OL,7,Fdisadvantaging those officers who did
OL,8,Fnot share Sergeant Sidhu's protected
OL,9,Fcharacteristic of race and who were
OL,10,Fdenied the opportunity to apply for
OL,11,Fthe role. It was not a proportionate
OL,12,Fmeans of achieving a legitimate aim."
OL,14,FAfter the written tribunal decision
OL,15,Fwas published, Thames Valley Police
OL,16,Fsaid it was committed to creating a
OL,17,Fworkplace "representative" of the
OL,18,Fcommunities it serves.
