OL,6,FMatthew Barber, Police and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner for the Thames Valley,
OL,8,Fsaid: "It is critical in building
OL,9,Fconfidence across our whole community
OL,10,Fthat there is never any discrimination
OL,11,Fin policing. In this case, the
OL,12,FEmployment Tribunal found that the
OL,13,FForce had discriminated against the
OL,14,Fclaimants on the basis of race. This
OL,15,Fis clearly unacceptable and should not
OL,16,Fhave happened.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
