OL,3,CForce 'considering next steps' after
OL,4,Cit discriminated against white officers
OL,6,F"I recognise Thames Valley Police's
OL,7,Fcommitment to building a workforce
OL,8,Fthat represents the whole community,
OL,9,Fbut it is apparent from the judgement
OL,10,Fthat the Force was wrong on this
OL,11,Foccasion in that the processes it
OL,12,Ffollowed were not fair, transparent,
OL,13,For competitive.
OL,15,F"I am clear that Thames Valley Police
OL,16,Fmust treat everyone equally when
OL,17,Fmaking appointments, determined solely
OL,18,Fon merit. I will ensure a full review
OL,19,Finto the processes, policies and
OL,20,Fapproach by the Force to ensure this
OL,21,Fcannot happen in the future.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
